_publ_section_synopsis
;
The bicyclic aromatic benzimidazolium cation stabilizes the layered perovskite
structure comprising inorganic {[SnI~4~]^2-^}<i>~n~</i> sheets. A
difluoro-substitution of the organic cation demonstrates the structural
versatility of the new approach.
;
_chemical_name_systematic
;
Poly[bis(benzimidazolium) [tetra-\m-iodido-stannate(II)]]
;
